Package ure.terrain

Interface UTerrain

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Blank, Door, Lava, Pit, Stairs, TerrainDeco, TerrainI, Water
    public interface UTerrain
    UTerrain defines all the public methods of terrain. It should not be implemented directly to create new custom terrain. Instead, TerrainDeco should be extended.
